{"tid":775382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西雅圖機場1飛機被盗飛後墜毀       2戰機曾升空攔截","createTime":"2018-08-11T06:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T23:30:27.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"52ec02435b1acaa6ea5fc500075e8cbaa6274643","tid":775382,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:20:52.000Z","msg":"西雅圖機場1飛機被盗飛後墜毀 2戰機曾升空攔截<br />\n<br />\n2018-08-11 13:04世界日報 即時報導<br />\n<br />\n據美國全國廣播公司報導，西雅圖塔科馬機場(Seattle-Tacoma International Airport)所有飛機現在停飛，因有不明身分人員偷了一架飛機，並在未得到空管許可的情況起飛。飛行員隨後威脅說將在空中做翻滾特技，2架F15戰機已經起飛進行了攔截。該架飛機傳已墜毀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦航空局發言人表示正在調查涉及西雅圖地區西塔科機場的「安全問題」。據美國全國廣播公司消息，阿拉斯加航空公司(Alaska Airlines)稱機上沒有乘客。更多信息有待確認。<br />\n&lt;聯合&gt;"},{"pid":"08a2615a6c25d4f7afc3eea2f1b9148d96e7e79e","tid":775382,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfa3c2c45fe0f809b04427ff276b4355360af7c","tid":775382,"uid":52706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:22:27.000Z","msg":"咁撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af36e8dd8cc375562f5c03052fd973191c0e4d1","tid":775382,"uid":106291,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:23:12.000Z","msg":"美國好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日都玩緊GTA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bcc1ab7ee8a21682c8e11b904516b00d51d968d","tid":775382,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:25:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"684fc17bdc3652f11de7dccb6536b12370545399","tid":775382,"uid":37912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:25:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55e575